root: ^A picture frame… What was the picture about?
^Something fun, like a party or a trip?
^My head hurts. Pain. I don’t want to remember.

c-0: ^I can picture… children. Mine? Or was I the child? When was it?
c-1: ^I went with someone, I think. But who?
c-2: ^But was it mine? It reminds me of true love, eternal love. But then, why can’t I remember?
